[
    {
        "text": "PowerPoint or any other program like that...",
        "startTime": 2883,
        "endTime": 5228,
        "slowStartTime": 4475,
        "slowEndTime": 8067
    },
    {
        "text": "...is one of the big problems that people have.",
        "startTime": 5719,
        "endTime": 8910,
        "slowStartTime": 8729,
        "slowEndTime": 13590
    },
    {
        "text": "So often I've heard people say, \"This is my presentation,\"...",
        "startTime": 9591,
        "endTime": 12407,
        "slowStartTime": 14537,
        "slowEndTime": 18836
    },
    {
        "text": "...and they show me this big stack of slides.",
        "startTime": 12811,
        "endTime": 15302,
        "slowStartTime": 19366,
        "slowEndTime": 23178
    },
    {
        "text": "That's not your presentation.",
        "startTime": 15691,
        "endTime": 16953,
        "slowStartTime": 23686,
        "slowEndTime": 25655
    },
    {
        "text": "You are the presentation.",
        "startTime": 17267,
        "endTime": 18947,
        "slowStartTime": 26050,
        "slowEndTime": 28645
    },
    {
        "text": "Those are just visual aids.",
        "startTime": 19178,
        "endTime": 20829,
        "slowStartTime": 28917,
        "slowEndTime": 31469
    },
    {
        "text": "When we work with people at Benjamin Ball Associates...",
        "startTime": 21791,
        "endTime": 23543,
        "slowStartTime": 32836,
        "slowEndTime": 35540
    },
    {
        "text": "...we often take away their PowerPoint to start with,...",
        "startTime": 23649,
        "endTime": 26382,
        "slowStartTime": 35623,
        "slowEndTime": 39798
    },
    {
        "text": "...get them to deliver their presentation, just them talking,...",
        "startTime": 26949,
        "endTime": 30729,
        "slowStartTime": 40573,
        "slowEndTime": 46318
    },
    {
        "text": "...and then afterwards, then we introduce the visual aids.",
        "startTime": 31076,
        "endTime": 35605,
        "slowStartTime": 46764,
        "slowEndTime": 53632
    },
    {
        "text": "So if you've got a speech coming up, or a talk or a presentation coming up,...",
        "startTime": 36064,
        "endTime": 39746,
        "slowStartTime": 54246,
        "slowEndTime": 59844
    },
    {
        "text": "...the worst thing you can do is switch on PowerPoint.",
        "startTime": 39922,
        "endTime": 42388,
        "slowStartTime": 60033,
        "slowEndTime": 63807
    },
    {
        "text": "Get a blank sheet of paper, plan what you're going to say,...",
        "startTime": 42887,
        "endTime": 46242,
        "slowStartTime": 64480,
        "slowEndTime": 69588
    },
    {
        "text": "...and then the very last thing you do is think,...",
        "startTime": 46668,
        "endTime": 48860,
        "slowStartTime": 70152,
        "slowEndTime": 73515
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"What visual aids can I use to help me get my point across?\"",
        "startTime": 49227,
        "endTime": 53901,
        "slowStartTime": 73991,
        "slowEndTime": 81076
    },
    {
        "text": "If you want an example of really bad use of PowerPoint, just go to any conference.",
        "startTime": 54428,
        "endTime": 60902,
        "slowStartTime": 81792,
        "slowEndTime": 91578
    },
    {
        "text": "Just sit there for a while,...",
        "startTime": 61195,
        "endTime": 62531,
        "slowStartTime": 91943,
        "slowEndTime": 94021
    },
    {
        "text": "...and very quickly you will see how not to do it.",
        "startTime": 62981,
        "endTime": 66754,
        "slowStartTime": 94621,
        "slowEndTime": 100356
    },
    {
        "text": "And if you're lucky you might get one or two speakers in a day who got it right.",
        "startTime": 67039,
        "endTime": 72162,
        "slowStartTime": 100708,
        "slowEndTime": 108468
    },
    {
        "text": "Your job, if you're trying to do something, is to emulate that one or two.",
        "startTime": 72481,
        "endTime": 76565,
        "slowStartTime": 108872,
        "slowEndTime": 115072
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't fall into the trap of producing lots of PowerPoint.",
        "startTime": 77175,
        "endTime": 80227,
        "slowStartTime": 115913,
        "slowEndTime": 120566
    }
]